Teltoli / Kit

*Teltoli snarls as Zardus doesn't do anything except threaten Iron Raptor, and fly off after Prowl. She flaps her wings, getting height, and zooms off after him. When she gets enough head wind, she tips her wings down and zooms down, her claws outstretched, aiming to dig her claws into his back and tackle him to the ground!*

=======

*Kit sniggers as Sinester shouts that he'll get her back. Yeah right. She sneaks up and sees the back of a bot (Nemesis Enforcer), which looked easy enough. She checked her weapons storage and took a few bounds, jumping on the back of his neck and shooting down point-blank at his neck!*
